## League of Nations (1920–1946)

**Société des Nations**

### 1920–1946

This isn't just some footnote in history; it was the first clumsy attempt at a global club, a grand experiment in international cooperation that, frankly, sputtered out like a damp match. Think of it as the awkward teenage years of global diplomacy – full of high ideals and epic failures.

